cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.SY, cs.LG, cs.AI

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language): The paper focuses on text-to-speech synthesis, which falls under the domain of natural language processing (NLP). 
- cs.SD (Sound): The paper deals with speech synthesis, which is a subfield of audio processing. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper presents an end-to-end system for speech synthesis, which involves multiple stages and components. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper uses a sequence-to-sequence framework and other machine learning techniques to train the speech synthesis model. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper presents a novel approach to speech synthesis using deep learning and generative models, which falls under the domain of AI.
